reviewText: I always enjoyed the roast and enjoyed this tape this many years later. I always fast forward thru Ruth Buzzi though as I never liked her skits anyway.
This is a real classic. George Burns and Jack Benny are two classic comedians. A must add to your collection.

This is a treasure...or at least ONE of the treasures in our humor library.
It's great to be able to "go back" to when comedy was really comedy.
